premise_source_doc_sentence: Charles Matthew Hunnam  (  born 10 April 1980  )  is an English actor .

claim: Green Street features Charlie Hunnam in its cast.
premise_source_doc_sentence: He is known for his roles as Jackson `` Jax '' Teller in the FX drama series Sons of Anarchy  (  2008 -- 14  )  , Nathan Maloney in the Channel 4 drama Queer as Folk  (  1999 -- 2000  )  , Lloyd Haythe in the Fox comedy series Undeclared  (  2001 -- 02  )  , the title role in Nicholas Nickleby  (  2002  )  , Pete Dunham in Green Street  (  2005  )  , Raleigh Becket in Pacific Rim  (  2013  )  , and in the title role of Guy Ritchie 's King Arthur : Legend of the Sword  (  2017  )  .
